```
@Override
public Receive createReceive() {
    return receiveBuilder()
      .match(CountWords.class, r -> {
          try {
              int numberOfWords = countWordsFromLine(r.line);
              getSender().tell(numberOfWords, getSelf());
          } catch (Exception ex) {
              getSender().tell(
               new akka.actor.Status.Failure(ex), getSelf());
               throw ex;
          }
    }).build();
}
```

